            <h3 style="font-size: 26px; color: #ff1493; margin: 40px 0 20px 0; font-weight: 700;">The Science Behind The Ingredients</h3>

            <p><strong>1. Himalayan Pink Salt</strong></p>
            <p>Contains 84 trace minerals including magnesium, potassium, and calcium that support hormone production and cellular metabolism. Unlike table salt, it doesn't cause water retention when used properly.</p>

            <p><strong>2. Green Tea Extract (EGCG)</strong></p>
            <p>Clinical studies show EGCG can boost metabolism by 17% and naturally activates GLP-1 receptors. One study published in the American Journal of Clinical Nutrition found significant fat oxidation improvements.</p>

            <p><strong>3. Berberine</strong></p>
            <p>Often called "nature's Ozempic," berberine has been shown in multiple peer-reviewed studies to improve insulin sensitivity and activate AMPK pathways. A 2008 study found it as effective as metformin for blood sugar control.</p>

            <p><strong>4. Resveratrol</strong></p>
            <p>This powerful antioxidant activates sirtuins (longevity genes) and supports mitochondrial function, leading to improved fat metabolism and energy production.</p>

            <p>To learn more about how Dr. Jastreboff discovered this unique combination and the full story behind the Pink Salt Trick breakthrough, <a href="https://moovonmkt.github.io/pink-salt-trick/" target="_blank"><strong>visit the original research article here</strong></a>.</p>

